      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine and no imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine state with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car performs exactly as it did when it first left the factory, with all systems functioning perfectly and a full service history available. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line.",
