      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project? This car is ready for a second chance! While it needs some mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's a fantastic opportunity for a DIY enthusiast or someone looking for a budget-friendly vehicle to restore. With some TLC, you can bring this diamond in the rough back to life!",
