    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains pristine, with every surface and feature in perfect, like-new condition. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained with a complete service history and zero signs of wear or age. This is a rare opportunity to own a top-tier vehicle that has been cared for at the highest level, offering both peak performance and an immaculate aesthetic.",
