    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive reliability, this vehicle has been curated for the driver who values both performance and fiscal prudence. It stands in commendable condition, having undergone a rigorous professional assessment to ensure mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Featuring a well-appointed interior and a robust service history, this offering provides a sophisticated driving experience without compromise. Secure an asset that balances long-term durability with immediate prestige.",
      "price": 32500.0,
