    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it! Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is super reliable and ready to go. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This unit boasts a broad torque curve and exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS rebuild and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with precision, transferring power to a functional M-Variable differential. Equipped with an upgraded cooling system and refreshed suspension bushings, this M3 maintains excellent lateral grip and high-speed stability. A driver-focused example that prioritizes mechanical performance and structural integrity.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly maintained. Clean title. Runs well. Reliable transportation.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior paint retains a beautiful gloss, with only a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches typical of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. The body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels are in excellent shape with no significant curbing. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the upholstery shows minimal wear on the bolsters and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All power features, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and infotainment system, are fully functional. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. We have kept a detailed service log, and the most recent oil change and multi-point inspection were completed just last month. The tires have roughly 70% tread remaining, ensuring you won't need a replacement any time soon. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, which exemplifies mechanical reliability and consistent performance. This selection has undergone a comprehensive professional assessment to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for roadworthiness and aesthetic presentation. Offering a balanced synthesis of durability and refined handling, this vehicle represents a premier investment for the discerning motorist seeking high-tier utility without compromise. Contact our representatives to arrange a private viewing of this exceptional automotive offering.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    }
